      "story_id": "hf:deepseek-ai/deepseek-v4-pro",
      "summary": "Technical Report👁️ We present a preview version of **DeepSeek-V4** series, including two strong Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) language models — **DeepSeek-V4-Pro** with 1.6T parameters (49B activated) and **DeepSeek-V4-Flash** with 284B parameters (13B activated) — both supporting a context length of **one million tokens**. DeepSeek-V4 series incorporate several key upgrades in architecture and optimization: 1. **Hybrid Attention Architecture:** We design a hybrid attention mechanism combining Compressed Sparse Attention (CSA) and Heavily Compressed Attention (HCA) to dramatically improve long-context efficiency. In the 1M-token context setting, DeepSeek-V4-Pro requires only **27% of single-token inference FLOPs** and **10% of KV cache** compared with DeepSeek-V3.2. 2. **Manifold-Constrained...",
